nodes.text: AT-TE 636 was an All Terrain Tactical Enforcer in the service of the Grand Army of the Republic that took part in the Second Battle of Geonosis.

AT-TE 636 was deployed with six other AT-TEs in General Kenobi's task force. When Kenobi's gunship was shot down, Waxer and Boil were dispatched to retrieve the wounded general, after they retrieved him, Commander Cody ordered the Walker to cover their retreat.
